          <p style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;">Were the topics in this newsletter important?</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;"><img src="assets/icon-heart_green.png" alt="" width="22" height="22" style="vertical-align:middle;border:0;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.example.com" style="color:#006837;font-weight:bold;" data-style-color data-style-href>Very important</a></p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;"><img src="assets/icon-thumbs-up.png" alt="" width="22" height="22" style="vertical-align:middle;border:0;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.example.com" style="color:#006837;font-weight:bold;" data-style-color data-style-href>Somewhat important</a></p>
