          <p style="font-size:16px;"><a href="https://www.example.com" style="color:#006837;font-weight:bold;" data-style-color data-style-href>E&amp;E News by Politico:</a> Most Americans Back Funding for the Massive Park Maintenance Backlog, Survey Finds</p>
