          <p>
            <br />
            You are receiving this email because you elected to receive marketing communications from
            Trust for Public Land under the terms of our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.
          </p>
          <p>
            You may unsubscribe from this list if you no longer wish to receive email marketing
            communications. If you would like to unsubscribe from ALL email communication from Trust for
            Public Land, request erasure or portability of your personal data please email
            donor.outreach@tpl.org with your request.
          </p>
          <p>
            You may not be able to save the whole world, but you can make a difference in your own
            backyard by planting a garden with native plants to provide a sustainable habitat for local
            pollinators and other wildlife.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
